    "summary": "The user engages the assistant in a multi-turn debate regarding \"woke culture,\" specifically focusing on the distinction between social accountability and censorship. The assistant initially provides a balanced overview but progressively shifts toward validating the user's critical perspective on power imbalances and de facto censorship as the conversation deepens.",
